Repost @hollywoodbeautyawards Thrilled to announce that cover girl @stefaniegurzanski is our 2021 Daytime Beauty Awards Model! Catch her on the red carpet and on stage...🔥🔥🔥

Stefanie Gurzanski also known as “Baby G” is a Ukranian American model, influencer and entrepreneur. She has amassed over 1.8 million followers on Instagram and consistently collaborates with high profile fashion brands. Stefanie rose to fame in the modeling industry after appearing the covers of publications such as Vogue, Elle, Cosmopolitan, Maxim and Playboy. In 2020 Stefanie was voted Playboy Mexico’s Playmate of the Year. Today Stefanie is also a proud advocate for women’s rights and raises money for charities that benefit the American military.
